ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]

(Size = 21), @p3='?' (DbType = Boolean), @p4='?' (Size = 128), @p5='?' (DbType = Int32), @p6='?' (DbType = Int32), @p7='?' (DbType = DateTime2), @p8='?' (DbType = Int64), @p9='?' (Size = 21), @p10='?' (DbType = Boolean), @p11='?' (Size = 128), @p12='?' (DbType = Int32), @p13='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']

MERGE [AbpPermissions] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, 0),

MERGE [AbpPermissions] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, 0),
(@p7, @p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, 1)) AS i ([CreationTime], [CreatorUserId], [Discriminator], [IsGranted], [Name], [RoleId], [TenantId], _Position) ON 1=0
